<!--<h4>First Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇaṁ bhujabaḷa praḍha<note n="272-1">Read prauḍha.</note>
<lb n="2"/>pratāpa cakrava rtri srī vīrarāmadēva rājyōdayada 18 <unclear>sārbba</unclear>dā<note n="272-2">The letter va is written above the line.</note>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ri sauvascharada puṣya sudha 8 vaḍavāradali śrīmatu sāyi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>seṭi mādauvege puṭṭida
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5"/>putra srī mūlasaṁgada sagaraṇada samaṁtabhadradēvara guḍḍa
<lb n="6"/>mādaiya <unclear>pajiyiṁ</unclear> muḍipi sidha gatiyaneydida srīvī
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tarāgāya maṁggaḷa mahā śrī śrī
</p>

